FlexibleBody
===========

Necessary:
===========
	- mbsim

Installation:
===========
	1. 
        aclocal
        autoheader
        libtoolize -c --force
        autoconf
        automake -a -c --force
			                
	2. 
		    ./configure

	      important options

  		  --prefix=PREFIX (where to install the library)
        -help (further options)
    
  3. 
        make

	4. 
        make install 
